      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Spaced Repetition and Memory"
        }
      ],
      "level": 1,
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Spaced repetition is a learning technique that reviews information at "
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "increasing intervals"
            }
          ],
          "type": "highlight"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": " to exploit the psychological spacing effect"
        },
        {
          "label": "ebbinghaus",
          "type": "footnote_ref"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "."
        }
      ],
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "The Forgetting Curve"
        }
      ],
      "level": 2,
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Without review, memories decay exponentially. Ebbinghaus showed that retention drops to about "
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "21%"
            }
          ],
          "type": "bold"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": " after 31 days without reinforcement."
        }
      ],
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "The forgetting curve follows approximately:"
        }
      ],
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "body": "R(t) = e^{-t/S}",
      "type": "math_block"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Where "
        },
        {
          "type": "inline_math",
          "value": "R"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": " is retention, "
        },
        {
          "type": "inline_math",
          "value": "t"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": " is time, and "
        },
        {
          "type": "inline_math",
          "value": "S"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": " is the stability of the memory."
        }
      ],
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
